Nka Emirates, Etihad Airways, Qatar Airways & Turkish Airlines, vyarakoze cane ibikorwa vyabo muri Afirika, hanyuma bigatuma ibisagara vyinshi bihambaye vy’Afirika bihuye n’ibindi vyigwa vy’ivy’ubuhinga vy’i Buraya.
Mu bihugu 30 vyo muri Afirika, Turkish Airlines usanga ari ho 2014.
Nimba ufise ikindi gihe co kugendera mu rugendo, nusuzume ingene uriko uravugwa muri Afirika ugereranywa n’urugendo rw’isi rw’isi.
Ntiwibagire kurushiriza kuronka amahera y’ibindi vy’amavisa, amakori y’ivy’urugendo, ibijanye n’ivy’urugendo, hamwe n’ibibanza vyose bivanye n’Afirika.
Nimba wipfuza guhunga hirya no hino kw’isi yose mu gihugu co mu Bumanuko, guhitamwo ibidukikije be n’ibibanza vyo gusa bitewe n’ukutagira amabarabara y’ivy’ibarabara.
Nta kibanza c’imiduga gihimbaza ivy’amazi vyose bitatu mu kiyaga c’i Bumanuko (kandi SkyTeam nta kintu na kimwe gihimbaza ivy’amazi).
Ariko rero, Star Alliance ishinga ibintu vyose, uretse igihugu ca Pacifique y’Epfo c’Epfo kiva muri Santiago de Chile gushika ku Tahiti, ico kikaba ari ikintu c’urugendo c’isi y’i LATAM One.
Ico kigwati si co kintu kimwe gusa nimba wipfuza guca mu burengerazuba bwa Amerika y’Epfo. ( Raba munsi y’aho)
Mu 1994, igihugu ca Nagorno-Karabakh c’Abanyarumeniya c’i Azerbajiyani cariko kirarwanya Azeris.
Ariko rero, nta n’ihanga rishinzwe, mbere n’i Armeniya, rirarimenya mu buryo bw’amategeko.
Ivyiyumviro vy’ivy’umubiri bijanye n’ico kibanza birabandanya guhonya ubucuti hagati ya Armeniya na Azerbajjan.
Intara y’i Kanali (Igihugu: Grachtengordel) ni intara izwi cane yo mu kinjana ca 17 ikikije Binnenstad ya Amsterdam.
Iyo ntara yose ivugwa ko ari ikibanza c’umurage w’isi w’UNUSCO c’agaciro kayo gadasanzwe k’imico kama be n’akahise, kandi imico kama yayo iri mu bihugu bihambaye kuruta ibindi vyose muri ico gihugu.
Cinque Terre, ivyo bisobanura ibihugu bitanu, birimwo ibisagara bitoyi bitanu vyo mu nkengera z’i Riomaggiore, i Manarola, i Corniglia, i Vernazza na Monterosso biri mu karere k’Umutaliyano ka Liguria.
Ivyo bivugwa ku rutonde rw’iryaga ry’isi ry’i UNESCO.
Mu binjana n’ibindi, abantu barabakanye bitonze ibibanza vyo mu gihugu c’uruzitiro, kigashika ku mabuye y’ikiyaga.
Inzira, amamoto be n’ubwato bifatanya n’ivyo bisagara, kandi amamoto ntashobora kubishikira avuye hanze.
Igifaransa kivugwa mu Bubiligi no muri Suwisi gitandukanye gatoyi n’ivy’Ubufaransa bivugwa mu Bufaransa, naho bimeze nk’uko bishoboka ko bitahukana.
Muri ico gifaransa, uburyo bw’igitigiri bwo mu gifaransa no mu Busuwisi burimwo ibintu bikeyi bitandukanye n’ubufaransa bwavuzwe mu Bufaransa, kandi amajambo amwamwe avuga atandukanye gatoyi.
Naho ari ukwo, abantu bose b’Abanyabelisiya bavuga igifaransa be n’Abasuwisi boba bari kumenya ivy’Ubufaransa mu vy’ishure, rero boshobora kugutahura n’igihe naho wakoresheje urutonde rw’ivy’igitigiri c’Umufaransa.
Mu mihingo myinshi y’isi, guhagarika umutima mwiza, kukaba kwerekana “amahoro. ”
Ariko rero, muri Malaysia, n’imiburiburi mu bihugu bimwebimwe vyo mu Burengerazuba, bisobanura “gushika, ” nk’ukwo gusa kw’impanwa ry’umubiri, ikintu gikoreshwa mu bihugu bimwebimwe vyo mu Burengerazuba, kandi kikaba gikwiye gukoreshwa gusa ku bw’ico kintu.
Muri ubwo buryo nyene, umugenzi w’Umungereza wo muri Esupanye yoshobora gushitsa ivyiyumviro vyerekeye igiti c’inguvu gihanganye n’icumba c’uwo muntu ariko ararushiriza kugarukira.
Ururimi rukoreshwa ni indimi z’ivy’ubucuruzi canke zibakwa zaremwe kugira ngo zirushiriza kuyaga hagati y’abantu bogoye kuvugana.
Batandukanye n’indimi zivugwa mu rurimi, zikaba ari indimi z’ivy’ibidukikije canke zikoreshwa mu buryo buhambaye cane ku bw’imvo zimwe canke zindi zikoreshwa mu kuyaga hagati y’ibindi ndimi.
Mu gihe c’ubushuhe bw’uwo musi, abagenzi barashobora gushikirwa n’ivyuma bituma amazi (canke ibindi).
Ivyo birashobora kuba biteye akaga nimba uwo mugenzo akurikirana uwo mugozi, akaba ariko araba inguvu z’agaciro maze akaguma amazi.
Mbere n’ubugaragwa bwiza kuruta ubundi bwose burashobora gushira cane mw’ijoro.
Mu ci, na canecane, uzokenera kwihweza impumuri nimba ufata ingingo yo kuja mu gisagara c’imvura.
N’igihe nyene uriko uragenda mu giti c’imvura c’ivy’amazi, amasogodi makeyi afise inzu mu gihe uja mw’imodoka ni umwanya uhagije wo kuja mu modoka.
Inyoni z’inkoni, canke indwara y’inkoni zirushiriza kure, zirashobora gutuma inyoni be n’ibikoko biba.
Ibintu bike birenga ibihumbi vyari bigeze bivugwa mu bantu, ariko bimwebimwe muri vyo vyarapfuye.
Benshi baragize abantu bakorera n’inkoni, mugabo kandi hariho akaga kamwe kari ku bacungezi b’inyoni.
Muri Noruwegi usanga ari ibibanza vyinshi be n’ibibanza bitewe n’igihugu bitewe n’ibibanza vyo mu kibanza kirengeye, kikaba kiruta n’ibindi.
Akenshi iyo micungararo ivugwa ko ari “impengamiro ” bisobanura ikibanza kinini, kitagira igiti, kikaba ari ikirere gikomeye.
I Rogaland be n’i Agder akenshi bavugwa ko ari “hei ” bisobanura igihugu gitagira igiti kirangurirwa gushira mu maso.
Ivyo bizotuma haba amasaha y’ivyuma, bikaba bishobora guhimbazwa n’imiyaga y’amasenyeri.
Amahome be n’amazu y’amazunga y’amazi arashobora guhunga maze amaguru ashobora guhagarika.
Ku ruhande rw’ibibumbe bikomeye vy’ivy’ivyuma vy’ivyuma bica bihuta, bica bigwa, kumbure bica bica bikagenda canke bigaca kure.
Ikiringo co kugendera ku bibanza vy’imisozi mu bisanzwe kiri mu ci c’Umuhindi.
Ariko rero, bari bafise ubwiza butandukanye n’ubwoko butandukanye mu gihe c’igihe c’imisozi, hakaba harimwo ibibanza vyinshi vy’imisozi vyinshi bironka ishavu vy’amagara be n’ugutanga ibikorwa nk’ivy’ivy’imisozi be n’ivy’ivy’ukuba.
Abantu bakeyi gusa ni bo baca baha amahera y’ivy’imiduga y’imiduga y’amavuka, ivyo bikaba bikaba bigaca bigaca bigaca bigatuma haba urugendo rw’amaziko rwo mu mininota ya nyuma.
Ivyo bintu birimwo Air Canada, Delta Air Lines, Lufthansa ku bijanye n’ivyumba biva muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika canke muri Kanada, be n’ivy’i WestJet.
Mu bihe vyose, utegerezwa gusohoka mu telefone ukoresheje ivy’umuduga.
